omen of the McMarrin!  It's just me Baxim with a few questions.  Maybe you experienced shaman could answer a few.<br>
     I've been looking at the shaman epic quest and was wondering if I'm at a high enough lvl to start it.  (Currently 36)  I have read the cheat sheet and think I can do the first few parts.  I could probably do the first three parts up untill the test of wisdom.  (Shield of falshood)  It looks like I may need help there.  I don't really know, seeing how I have never seen or herd of this done solo.<br>
     Well, what do ya think?  Please give me a tell in game or leave a message here if you have any tips or could give me a hand.  <br>
Thanks all and rock on.<br>
<br>
sincerely,<br>
<br>
Baxim Goodfight<br>
36 shaman<br>
Proud follower of the clan McMarrin.<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#ffffff><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub34.ezboard.com/urichardwith.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Richardwith</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>ezOP</span><br> <font color=#6F6F6F>(5/9/01 8:11:34 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> hrm</span><hr size=1> well, first part of quest is simple and takes about an hour to do with a porter. Test of wisdom is also very easy to complete. <br>
<br>
When you get to the Test of patience you will need some outside help. First off when you sit at the bottom of Eruds xing for the spirits to spawn the Killer sharks will path by you, Dagelrod, Myself and Renna were all killed by one, which later ended in a GM summon for me. Second time around we got it. After getting your gem from the spirits head to Rathe Mountains where you will need to kill two mobs, one a paladin, the second a SK, or you can simply buy their items in EC, Woe, Envy and Shield. head to WK and turn them, and you have the shield.<br>
<br>
The test of might and the rest I would recommend being at least 45+ to complete. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#ffffff><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub34.ezboard.com/bmcmarrin.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=baximgoodfight>Baxim Goodfight</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#6F6F6F>(5/10/01 10:36:35 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: hrm</span><hr size=1> Hello again.<br>
<br>
     Last night I compleeted the first two parts of the quest, now it's time for the test of patience.  My question is what lvl do I need to be to protect myself from the sharks?  Would it be wize to group up with my brother Barnebus?  You know for protection.  (hehe)  I'm not sure Ghash has compleeted this test.  He was trying last night as I was trying to catch up to him.  I did loose track of him 'cause I had to walk the stinking dog about 15,000 times that night.  If Ghash hasn't done it yet I'm sure we would be fine right?<br>
     As far as the MM part with the Dire wolves I will try to get to lvl 45 before I ask for the guilds help.  Just wondering where I should hunt now?  Looking for fast exp.  Hehe although aren't we all.<br>
     Anyway, thanks for the help and may the force be with you!<br>
Sincerely,<br>
<br>
Baxim Goodfight<br>
36 level shaman<br>
Servant of the McMarrin  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#ffffff><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub34.ezboard.com/urichardwith.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Richardwith</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>ezOP</span><br> <font color=#6F6F6F>(5/10/01 10:46:05 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> hmm</span><hr size=1> The sharks are meanies to put it simply, they hit hard, fast and have a fair amount of hp to boot. I believe you, Ghash and barney could do it, maybe have tyle with you for evac and porting. Secondly only one of you can do it in a 2 hour period. Everytime gooma, or whatever that fat ogres name swims out to the spirits it takes 2 hours for her to respawn. So be prepared to hang around Eruds Xing or a second spawn or you guys might have to choose who goes first.<br>
<br>
<br>
Richerd <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#ffffff><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub34.ezboard.com/utimlaake.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Timlaake</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#6F6F6F>(5/11/01 2:52:54 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Quit complaining about the dog</span><hr size=1> I'll be home in Davenport this weekend so I won't be back on till the following monday, but Baxim will get to play more because I will have our dog to take care of.<br>
<br>
Barnebus out <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub34.ezboard.com/fmcmarrinfrm1.showMessage?topicID=94.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub34.ezboard.com/fmcmarrinfrm1.showMessage?topicID=86.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub34.ezboard.com/fmcmarrinfrm1.emailToFriend?topicID=90.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub34.ezboard.com/fmcmarrinfrm1.threadControl?topicID=90.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/rust/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub34.ezboard.com/fmcmarrinfrm1.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=90.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub34.ezboard.com/fmcmarrinfrm1.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=90.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub34.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="mcmarrinfrm1">General<option value="mcmarrinfrm2">Stories<option value="mcmarrinfrm3">Auction<option value="mcmarrinfrm4">Raid Schedule<option value="mcmarrinfrm5">Officers<option value="mcmarrinfrm6">McMarrin Tavern</select></td><td><input type=submit value="Go" class=inputbutton></td></tr></table></form></td></tr></table><br><font color=#6F6F6F>- </font><a href=http://pub34.ezboard.com/bmcmarrin>McMarrin</a><font color=#6F6F6F> - </font><a href=http://pub34.ezboard.com/fmcmarrinfrm1>General</a> <f